  </inputs>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="spec FR-05">KEEP `sprk_analysisactiontype` lookup table (decorative role; maker categorization). `sprk_executoractiontype` field on lookup table rows remains but is advisory only (not load-bearing). Acceptance: table preserved; doc note added that runtime ignores the field.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec NFR-08">Documentation discipline — DELETE outdated, UPDATE current. NO SUPERSEDED markers, NO redirect stubs, NO archive folders. PR review gates drift.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec Q4 RESOLVED">Lookup-table fate: REPURPOSE as decorative for maker browsing. NOT dropped.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-013">BFF AI Architecture — runtime dispatch lives on `node.sprk_executortype` only. Lookup table is informational, not load-bearing.</constraint>
    <constraint source="CLAUDE.md §11">No new component, no new doc file in this task (Wave 6 task 062 may consolidate further). In-place update only.</constraint>
    <constraint source="bff-extensions.md">Doc-only task; no BFF source change; no publish-size impact.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ownership-boundary">DO NOT modify `docs/architecture/ai-architecture-consumer-routing.md` (chat-routing-redesign-r1 owns; READ-ONLY in R7 per project CLAUDE.md).</constraint>
